{"titre":"a_tattoo_boom_in_brooklyn","sousTitre":"Ink ink everywhere","consigne":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p>","videoUrl":"https://player.vimeo.com/external/146004133.sd.mp4?s=3fb6330b943d7f6169d8990da4a3e056ebe1026d&profile_id=112","btnOutil":{"format":1,"liste":[{"etiquette":"","fonction":"impression"},{"etiquette":"","fonction":"--"},{"etiquette":"","fonction":"--"},{"etiquette":"","fonction":"--"},{"etiquette":"","fonction":""}]},"clavier":"","scenario":{"accesQ":"0","qoAccesC":"3","msgAE":"","verrCorr":"1"},"pages":[{"titre":"Being different","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Being different","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>In which borough of New York City are we here?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Right or wrong?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Getting tattooed in that part of town definitely makes you different</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Brooklyn (Williamsburg and Greenpoint) :</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>«Greenpoint is the northernmost neighborhood in the New York City borough of Brooklyn. It is bordered on the southwest by Williamsburg...» </span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>source: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenpoint,_Brooklyn</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Wrong: «if you want to stand out from the crowd in Brooklyn's Williamsburg and Greenpoint neighbourhoods, getting a tattoo won't get you very far»</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"1.08","fin":"12.41","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Meet Jeb","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Meet Jeb","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>In which neighbourhood is Jed's tattoo parlour?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>How long has it been there?</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Williamsburg</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>16 years</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"12.23","fin":"19.33","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}},{"type":"qo","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"Nouvelle question","extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"},"txtCorrection":"","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"0","fin":"0","affichA":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Tattoos rule OK","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Tattoos rule OK","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>   - Find one adjective and one sentence that refer to how tattoos are viewed in this neighbourhood</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>   - Right or wrong?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- There are more and more tattooed kids</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>-Jeb approves of this</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>«This neighbourhood's always been pretty &lt;I&gt;tattoo friendly...&lt;/I&gt;»</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>«...I would say this is definitely &lt;I&gt;the most tattooed neighbourhood in New York&lt;/I&gt;»</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Right:«You do see more like younger kids with a lot of tattoos...»</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Wrong:«...which is pretty insane...»</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"19.64","fin":"35","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Exodus","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Exodus","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>A lot of tattoo artists have come to settle in Greenpoint and Williamsburg :</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- How long has this «exodus» been going on?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Which borough did they come from?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Why did they leave?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- fifteen years</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Manhattan</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- the rents were too high</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- a dozen</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: initial;'>«</span><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 1.1em; background-color: initial;'>Over the last fifteen years, Greenpoint and Williamsburg have attracted a host&nbsp;</span><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 1.1em; background-color: initial;'>of tattoo artists fleeing the high retail rents</span><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 1.1em; background-color: initial;'>&nbsp;in Manhattan, »</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>* a host : an army</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>&nbsp;retail rent: the price one has to pay monthly to rent premises for a shop</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"34.89","fin":"43.1","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Settling down","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Settling down","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Has this exodus led to the opening of many new tattoo parlours?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>How does the reporter describe their clientele?</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Yes: <i>over a dozen</i> new shops have scattered around the neighbourhoods</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- art-and tattoo-loving</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"43.01","fin":"49.27","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"A particular brand of customers","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"A particular brand of customers","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Tattoo artists have to provide high-quality work because the people here are different: give 3 pieces of information about them</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- they are young</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- they have art related occupations: artists, film-makers, graffiti artists, writers</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- they have taste, they often bring their own designs, you have to work with them</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- they are very picky (= demanding)</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"49.3","fin":"82.45"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":0,"fin":0}}]},{"titre":"Inspiration for a project","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Inspiration for a project","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>These people have two contradictory traits, what are they?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Some of them have been the inspiration for a project: </span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Which category of tattoed people?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- What sort of project?</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- picky but carefree (=easygoing; in French: insouciant)</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- a book of photographs</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- they have tattoos all over their bodies</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>'They may be <i>picky </i>about their tattoos but it was the neighbourhood's <i>carefree attitude</i> to getting inked all over that inspired <i>photographer</i>&nbsp;Paul Nathan to create a book of portraits depicting the<i> full-body art&nbsp;</i>&nbsp;of local residents...'</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"82.06","fin":"98.07","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Seizing the opportunity","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Seizing the opportunity","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Decide which is true:</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>1) Paul decided to do this project because of the many tattoos all around </span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>2) Paul looked for tattoos because he had decided to do a project about tattoos</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>1) is closer to the truth:</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 1.1em; background-color: initial;'>«you can't help but notice all the wonderful tattoos on the street, and then I was really looking for a project, and I thought «Well it's right on the doorstep» and it'd be a great thing to do»</span><br></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"98.02","fin":"109.01","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"A shift?","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"A shift?","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Complete with adjectives or past participles:</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Paul was ....................... at the openness with which people agreed to be ...............</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>for the book; he says they feel ...................... to express themselves, he also</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'> thinks that it is now ............................... to heavily tattoo yourself. According to</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'> Paul, society's making a shift, everyone is now ..................</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>surprised, photographed, free, acceptable, tattooed</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"109.37","fin":"137.5","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Willamsburg's rapid development","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Willamsburg's rapid development","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Match these numbers: <strong>131, 12, 2</strong>  with the following data:</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>a- the period covered by the reporter's analysis</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>b- the percentage by which house prices rose over this period</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>c- the number of times by which household incomes have been multiplied</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>a: 12; b: 131; c: 2</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'><i>«Over the last 12 years Williamsburg has experienced rapid development, with average household incomes almost doubling and house prices rising 131%»</i></span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"137.47","fin":"147.7","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"business is booming","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"business is booming","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Choose the correct answers:</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>The community has <i>grown / shrunk</i> considerably and artists have <i>more / less</i>&nbsp;work now</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Quote two comparative forms you can hear that justify your choices</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>grown, more</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>With the growth of the community, tattoo artists have gotten <i>busier</i></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'><i>More people</i>&nbsp;equals&nbsp;<i>more clientele</i></span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"148.12","fin":"162.19","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Working conditions","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Working conditions","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Give 2 out of three pieces of information about tattoo artists in this passage</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- What is the solution as they face competition?</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- they can be selective about the type of work they do /  some hold waiting lists of several months... /  ... commanding rates of up to $200 an hour  </span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Do the best work they can, do better tattoos</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"162.48","fin":"186.09","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"More acceptance","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"More acceptance","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Attitudes towards tattoos have changed over the years; complete : </span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Now it is ......................, people are ......................... about what they represent.</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>In the past they were the attributes of ...............</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Kamio's father thinks he's ...................... but he likes his son's tattoos, he finds</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'> they look .............. ; but his  grandmother may get ................. about them.</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>accepted, curious,</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>criminals</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>crazy, cool, angry<strong>*</strong></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'><strong></strong></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'><strong>*</strong> He thinks his grandmother may «flip out», which is a familar way of saying «lose her temper»</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"186.33","fin":"214.1","affichA":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"}}]},{"titre":"Restrictions","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"Restrictions","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Despite the rise in popularity of full-body art and tattoos, most artists won't just tattoo anyone anywhere.</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>-What age group is Jeb referring to, do you think?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>- Why does he think they should be careful?</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Complete: </span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>You shouldn't have highly visible tattoos ........ you're very covered.</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Young people: &lt;I&gt;we're no one's father or mother... they're kind of jumping the gun, that's kind of a new fashion thing but they'll pay for it like ten years on when they cannot get a job&lt;/I&gt;</span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p><p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>unless (= if...not)</span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"214.24","fin":"245.64"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":0,"fin":0}}]},{"titre":"","questions":[{"type":"qo","titre1":"","titreQ":"","txtQuestion":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'>Watch again and write a few lines about Paul's and Jeb's opinions. Who do you agree with most?</span></p>","txtCorrection":"<p style='text-align:left'><span style='text-size:12;color:#444444;'></span></p>","extraitCorrection":{"debut":"0","fin":"0"},"extraitQuestion":{"debut":0,"fin":0}}]}],"moduleId":"oX6GLnIT","interface":{"couleur1":"#932846"},"tempsPon":1477555620000,"sousTitrage1":""}